cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.HC, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the security threats posed by phishing attacks and proposes solutions to combat them. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the impact of phishing attacks on the Internet of Things (IoTs), which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CY (Computers and Society). The paper also discusses end-user awareness, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper proposes solutions to protect users from phishing attacks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
